{"tid":890153,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先俾女神煎咗巴","createTime":"2018-11-05T06:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T10:59:17.000Z","uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2a2804af646024b0faa4007467253d82f2072f3e","tid":890153,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:00:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，最近天氣凍，有鼻敏感嘅我最近成日鼻塞，頭先食飯有條女走嚟搭枱，心諗都係見我靚仔先走埋嚟搭枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，咁多位唔坐係要坐埋嚟，咁我見搭枱條女幾正心諗有食唔食罪大惡極<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，咁我咪膽粗粗問佢：你有冇line，點知佢遮住心口煎咗我一巴：賤格！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  餐飯錢都冇俾就走咗，我都明嘅，第一次約會男仔俾錢係正路嘅，但煎巴我意思係咩？係咪我太進取？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667555696f7995e06598fcbeb091a0c9055ffa53","tid":890153,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:01:27.000Z","msg":"佢怕醜姐"},{"pid":"e04cf67ddcb96903587b08004a46ec76f42107a0","tid":890153,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:01:50.000Z","msg":"宜家塊面仲有個手印，有冇人知點樣靠手印搵返條女？"},{"pid":"e585ddd878523b447b94909fd6c018393b6969b6","tid":890153,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"667555696f7995e06598fcbeb091a0c9055ffa53","tid":890153,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:01:27.000Z","msg":"佢怕醜姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:02:58.000Z","msg":"又係，睇得出佢份人保守，個bra都係淨色啡色嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3dc3427e044a1b28f0c234ac53dd970de7f30a","tid":890153,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f